  "body": "Resources like Deployment, ReplicaSet, and DaemonSet should, as a best practice, declare `selector.matchLabels` rules in their pod template:\r\n\r\nhttps://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/tools/kubectl/object-management-using-declarative-config/#defining-controller-selectors-and-podtemplate-labels\r\n\r\nDoing so prevents a number of odd-ball cases where pods are not appropriately updated.\r\n\r\nWe should write a linting rule to catch this case.",
